{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":303900,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3039_00_01","textHome":"我是三穗野星罗，打算成为一名电影导演。我@现在是工匠学舍得历史研究部的一员。不过@，完全没有在做历史的研究就是了…。立志@做一名电影导演的契机，是小时候看了一部@怪兽电影，受到了冲击。不过，我也并不是@打算做一名专门拍怪兽电影的导演哦！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"id":303900,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_013.exp.json","id":303900,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":303900}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":303900,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.9,"chara":[{"id":303900,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303900,"motion":100}]}],"group_10":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":303900,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3039_00_17","textHome":"拍摄的时候我一直都在观察大家的状况的哦。@导演是要去统筹剧组成员和演员的人，没有@威望的话可是当不成的哦？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":303900,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"id":303900,"motion":100}]}],"group_11":[{"autoTurnFirst":8.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303900,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3039_00_18","textHome":"之前我就一直在想了…我变身的时候的衣服，@总感觉有点像怪兽啊？我可没记得自己有许@愿过想要成为怪兽呢~？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303900,"motion":300}]}],"group_12":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303900,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3039_00_19","textHome":"啊，好像能行。下次给你展示一些能更上镜的@技巧！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":303900,"motion":0}]}],"group_13":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303900,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3039_00_20","textHome":"我之前还以为，变强应该是更有那种，哐——@！一下子的感觉呢"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":303900,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303900}]}],"group_14":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":303900,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3039_00_21","textHome":"作为魔法少女的升级，也意味着作为电影导演@的成长！因为导演就是份给观众布下魔法的@工作吧！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"id":303900,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":303900,"motion":1}]}],"group_15":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":303900,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3039_00_22","textHome":"变身！嗷呜——！大怪兽三穗野大人降临了！@…虽然外表不可能变成那样，但我的内在还@是成长了很多的哦。反正就等下次战斗的时@候看着吧"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.7,"chara":[{"id":303900,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.9,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_013.exp.json","id":303900,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":303900}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.2,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":303900,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":303900,"motion":100}]}],"group_16":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303900,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3039_00_23","textHome":"哇——，有种至今为止从未有的感觉！有了一@种下次战斗一定能行的自信哦！拍摄完足以@留名青史的杰作的巨匠们，一定也是这样的@心情！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":303900,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.2,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":303900,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":303900}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_013.exp.json","id":303900}]}],"group_17":[{"autoTurnFirst":0.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303900,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3039_00_24","textHome":"哦，你来了！我刚刚在鉴赏电影。因为巨匠的@作品，全是值得我参考的地方！怎么样，要@一起看吗？虽然是从中途看起了！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":303900}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"id":303900,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_013.exp.json","id":303900,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":303900,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":303900,"motion":100}]}],"group_18":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":303900,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3039_00_25","textHome":"早上好！你问我？我是早早起来，正在调整相@机呢！马上就结束了，你在那儿坐会儿！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303900}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_013.exp.json","id":303900,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":303900,"motion":0}]}],"group_19":[{"autoTurnFirst":7.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":303900,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3039_00_26","textHome":"父母总是给我唠叨“好好自己做饭”，所以我@每天都自己做便当…这个，可真是比想象的@要麻烦的多！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303900,"motion":300}]}],"group_2":[{"autoTurnFirst":7.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":303900,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3039_00_02","textHome":"我是三穗野星罗，是工匠学舍高中部的高一年@级学生，也是历史研究部的一员…！但这些@都不过是避世人耳目的身份！将来的梦想是@…当一名电影导演哦！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":303900,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":303900}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"id":303900,"motion":100}]}],"group_20":[{"autoTurnFirst":8.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303900,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3039_00_27","textHome":"现在突然感到有一些不安…我应该没有忘了预@约录像了吧…？今天的“Zmic Zon@e”…"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":303900,"motion":0}]}],"group_21":[{"autoTurnFirst":8.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303900,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3039_00_28","textHome":"我想想，餐具也收拾好了，接下来就是扫地了@呢…我因为是一个人，每到这个时间，必须@去把家务都给好好做了才行呢"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":303900,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":303900,"motion":100}]}],"group_22":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":303900,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3039_00_29","textHome":"Scene 7, Cut 2, Take@ 3！Start！…嗯，声音好好地发出@来了！啊，这个是预演。为了能在外景拍摄@的时候能大声叫出来！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"id":303900,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":303900,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303900}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":303900,"motion":100}]}],"group_23":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_013.exp.json","id":303900,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3039_00_30","textHome":"有时候会看魔女的攻击看的走神呢…哇！这个@像怪兽一样！看起来就很疼！但是好帅！这@样。虽然不是去想这些的时候就是"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303900,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":303900,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303900,"motion":300}]}],"group_24":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_013.exp.json","id":303900,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3039_00_31","textHome":"其他魔法少女的战斗方式，都很有电影的感觉@很帅气，看着非常能起参考作用…啊，不是@说自己的战斗方式的参考，而是电影演出的@参考哦"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":303900,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.9,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303900,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":303900,"motion":200}]}],"group_25":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303900,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3039_00_32","textHome":"怎么好像聚集了这么多魔法少女在这？这是在@拍什么？那我想作为导演参加…不行？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":303900,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303900}]}],"group_26":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303900,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3039_00_33","textHome":"电影以外的兴趣？有的哦。电视剧我也喜欢，@网络播放的电视剧我也有在看哦！都是一样@的？说起来确实呢…哈哈哈哈！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":303900,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"id":303900,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303900}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_013.exp.json","id":303900,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":303900}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"id":303900,"motion":0}]}],"group_27":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303900,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3039_00_34","textHome":"每次准备逞强的时候都会被古町前辈发怒道“@请考虑后果三思而行”，可我也是思考了很@多的啊…虽然只会在在行动过后思考…"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":303900}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303900}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.9,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":303900,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303900,"motion":300}]}],"group_28":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":303900,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3039_00_35","textHome":"啊，这个pose很棒！我马上拿相机来，你@就在这不要动可以吗？因为这可以成为拍摄@的时候的构图的参考！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"id":303900,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_013.exp.json","id":303900}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"id":303900,"motion":1}]}],"group_29":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_013.exp.json","id":303900,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3039_00_36","textHome":"这个地点，你怎么看？…不是，我是说看上去@挺适合做外景拍摄的…不是怪兽电影哦!?@恋爱电影之类的！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":303900,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303900,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":303900,"motion":100}]}],"group_3":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303900,"motion":0,"pos":1,"soulGem":0,"voice":"vo_char_3039_00_03","textHome":"这啥？如假包换的宇宙生物？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"id":303900,"motion":400}]}],"group_30":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":303900,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3039_00_37","textHome":"电视剧与纠葛！壮丽的奇观！化虚构为现实的@最新技术！怪兽电影饱含电影的精华，卓别@林也是这么说的！…我骗人的"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"id":303900,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"id":303900,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.7,"chara":[{"id":303900,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":303900,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":303900}]}],"group_31":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303900,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3039_00_38","textHome":"欸…什么？抱歉，我在用手机看电影。嗯——@…虽然这个手机是比较大的了，还是不够有@场面感呢。能不能通过历史研究部买一台投@影仪呢…"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":303900,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303900,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303900,"motion":1}]}],"group_32":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":303900,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3039_00_39","textHome":"之前，让吉良学姐试了